See the "User's Manual" for info on "Getting Started" in ParFlow.

To build a linux version without MPI for sequential runs:

./build -arch linux -comm seq install

To build a Linux version with MPI for sequential runs:

./build -arch linux -comm mpi1 install

To build a Linux version for the CASC cluster (tcl is not in default location):

./build -config $PARFLOW_SRC/config/linux.casc.config install

To build on GPS

./build install

To build a version of parflow with Purify:

build -arch purify -g  -config /home/ssmith/parflow/src/config/solaris.purify.config install

